sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Browser
    participant Server
    participant Stripe
    
    User->>Browser: Click checkout
    Browser->>Server: POST /pay
    Browser->>Browser: Show loading spinner
    Server->>Stripe: charge()
    Stripe-->>Server: Success token
    Server-->>Browser: Success response
    Browser->>Browser: Stop loading spinner
    Browser->>User: Show success screen